    "description": "Hatsuho Shouji Co.,Ltd. trades in steel and construction materials in Japan. The company offers interior building materials, such as steel ceiling framing, steel wall base, gypsum board, glass wool, and residential insulation materials, as well as ceiling, non-combustible board, rock wool sound-absorbing panels, bis, suspension bolts, ceiling access and underfloor inspection hatch, trim molding and glass container, bathroom ceiling panel joiner, PVC ceiling trim/magar, PVC angle joiner, wallpaper base corner, aluminum ceiling trim and angles, aluminum joiner, ceiling looper, glue, deck hanging bracket, spandrel, soundproofing sheet and partitions, soundproofing panels, rock wool, OA floors, steel flooring material, insulation panel, lead board, royal stud, helmet, hangall, picture rail, welding machine, LVL, nonkiriko, and machine tools. It also provides exterior products, such as carports, sheds, fences, and stone materials to house builders and exterior construction companies; and water-based glass shatterproof coating, LED, non-flammable lightweight ceiling, seismic isolation and control system, and flood control solutions. In addition, the company offers housing and environment-related products, including colored steel sheets, solar power roofing, ALC metal fittings and auxiliary materials, and ceramic building material fittings and auxiliary materials, as well as architectural hardware, welded wire mesh, and iron wire products. Further, it provides metal siding, rain gutters, sandwich panels, sheet metal tools, galvalume steel roofing and exterior wall molding; ceiling lighting fixtures, industrial pressure fan, battery storage, drill screws, polycarbonate corrugated sheet, sheet metal mounting hardware, metal joiner, rooftop ventilation fan, cutting wheel; nails, screws, breathable sheet, anchor bolts, bicycle rack, nameplate, binding wire, grating; and annealed wire products. Hatsuho Shouji Co.,Ltd. was founded in 1946 and is headquartered in Nagoya, Japan."
